column5: I will be going to halleys camp next september. I plan on staying atcaribou falls any fishing reports for the area, or advice I have stayed there about 10 years ago, it's been awhile. thanks flip
what are you fishing for? Good walleye that time of year.

I will be fishing for wally and northern Pike, I am a little familar with the area would just like some info on any thing you can provide. I will be flying from Germany next September, Iam currently in the U.S army living overseas and there is no good fishing over here. Thanks Flip
drop me an e mail [email protected] I could tell you some of the water we fish and what to look for.Although I fish it mostly in the spring I have been around for the fall bite
